title: music for VGHD
description:
Some sound clips to go along with vghd.

If these files are too large (the repeats are repetitions of the best part of the songs for unlimited times), just download the non-amplified versions and the wav or mp3 versions of particular sounds from the 'sounds' folders. 

Then use Audacity to generate the desired effects. Drag and drop on audacity; align properly by checking with magnification. Upload your creativity on torrents.

Some Weapon sounds thrown in just for fun. You can probably use this during sound testing too.

Music works with 1.0.4.756 and probably above.
